title: NFL Around the League: NFC West - August 30th, 2013
itunes:title: NFL Around the League: NFC West - August 30th, 2013
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling give you their picks for 2013 NFL Defensive Player of the Year and break down the NFC West. Also, Wesseling challenges Twitter hopefuls in trivia for his prized NFL toaster. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL for your chance to join the show.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
